This is a '''list of national parks of Belarus'''. It also lists main [[nature reserve]]s.

There are currently four [[national park]]s in [[Belarus]]. The [[Białowieża Forest|Belavezhskaya Pushcha National Park]] is a trans-boundary park between [[Belarus]] and [[Poland]]. Together parks cover more than {{convert|3300|km2|sqmi|abbr=on}}.

